name: FVX's Unique Checkpoint Model 1
description:
Hi, this is a checkpoint merge of several models. Notably it's an older verion, but still great.

List:

-Chilloutmix

-Lofi

-Realistic v13

-SeekArtMega

-Grapefruit

-HM? hentai mode? not sure???

It's a 70/30 mix so 70% realism and 30% anime.
